      <title>马拉维认为，随着消费者价格上涨28.5％，通货膨胀率是通货膨胀的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/malawi-sees-a-pickup-in-inflation-as-consumer-prices-rise-28-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马拉维在一月份的通货膨胀率上升，因为它继续应对埃尔尼诺（El Nino）诱发的南部非洲国家造成的粮食不安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/malawi-sees-a-pickup-in-inflation-as-consumer-prices-rise-28-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 14:20:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
